{"tid":985114,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"上網求愛！31歲女想找真愛...「po大露乳溝照」公開徵男友！眼尖網：激似電影女配...","createTime":"2019-01-17T10:36:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-17T13:08:55.000Z","uid":212399,"like":3,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c71386bf6dee2cb7e3bc94ccd81f178ae7ca1ac1","tid":985114,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T10:36:43.000Z","msg":"每個人的心中都渴望愛！<br />\n尼日利亞一位女子為了徵男友，將自己大露乳溝的照片po上網！<br />\n據《tori》報導，尼日利亞31歲女子昆&middot;奧卡福，在當地具有一定的知名度，因為他是全尼日利亞「毛髮最多」的女人，<br />\n不僅有意投濃密蓬鬆的頭髮、甚至還有落腮鬍及些微的胸毛。<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.candymush.com/201901/PhY5WSze.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.candymush.com%2F201901%2FPhY5WSze.jpg&h=00020542&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.candymush.com/201901/jiWeit0Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.candymush.com%2F201901%2FjiWeit0Y.jpg&h=be7bd957&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n昆幾年前還常常跟一名英俊的小鮮肉約會合照，不過她日前在Instagram上分享自己的乳溝照片，還說單身中想要找真愛，看來似乎已經跟該名小鮮肉分手了。<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.candymush.com/201901/axx7t1kE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.candymush.com%2F201901%2Faxx7t1kE.jpg&h=199e4607&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n越看越覺得昆有些眼熟，有人跟揪揪一樣想起了「大娛樂家」裡，<br />\n歌聲神之渾厚洪亮的鬍子女嗎~<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.candymush.com/201901/fHJVO9HE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.candymush.com%2F201901%2FfHJVO9HE.jpg&h=5e7b4760&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.candymush.com/201901/qFJnyjCS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.candymush.com%2F201901%2FqFJnyjCS.jpg&h=f2dbd82a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n相似度超高XDDD<br />\n看來這是一位對自己相當有自信的女子~<br />\n<a href=\"http://candymush.com/?c=149079\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcandymush.com%2F%3Fc%3D149079&d=3m4rN%2F1AIvPT8ELKuhEPHv755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=f6857467\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://candymush.com/?c=149079</a>"},{"pid":"02a68f7640f5af